## 4. Frontmatter schema

**Mandatory fields in every document:**

```yaml
---
type: <see table below>
title: "Readable title"
slug: "slug-kebab-case"
status: draft | in-review | accepted | active | done | archived
phase: "00" | "01" | "02" | "03" | "04" | "05" | "06" | "07"
created: YYYY-MM-DD
updated: YYYY-MM-DD
generated_by: sdlc-<skill-name>
owner: "{{OWNER}}"
tags: [<tag1>, <tag2>]
---
```

**`type` values by folder:**

| Folder | Valid `type` |
|---|---|
| 00-steering/ | `steering-product`, `steering-tech`, `steering-standards` |
| 01-planning/prd/ | `prd` |
| 01-planning/epics/ | `epic` |
| 01-planning/milestones/ | `milestone` |
| 02-architecture/adr/ | `adr` |
| 02-architecture/c4/ | `c4-context`, `c4-container`, `c4-component` |
| 02-architecture/trd/ | `trd` |
| 02-architecture/api/ | `api-rest`, `api-grpc`, `api-async`, `api-webhook` |
| 03-domain/ | `context-map`, `ubiquitous-language`, `aggregate`, `domain-event`, `contract` |
| 04-specs/<feature>/ | `spec-requirements`, `spec-design`, `spec-tasks` |
| 05-development/ | `worktree`, `branch` |
| 06-design-system/ | `ds-token`, `ds-component`, `ds-pattern` |
| 07-retrospectives/ | `retro`, `review`, `incident`, `incident-lessons` |

**Additional relevant fields (by type):**

- `adr`: `decision_date`, `supersedes`, `superseded_by`
- `epic`: `prd`, `milestone`, `estimate`
- `spec-*`: `feature`, `epic`
- `incident`: `severity` (SEV1-4), `detected_at`, `mitigated_at`, `resolved_at`, `mttr_minutes`
- `api-*`: `auth`, `version`

