## 5. Phase map

| Folder | Responsibility |
|---|---|
| `00-steering/` | Product vision, technical principles, team standards (Kiro-style) |
| `01-planning/` | PRDs, epics (with embedded stories), milestones |
| `02-architecture/` | ADRs, C4 diagrams, TRDs (cross-feature), API contracts |
| `03-domain/` | DDD: context-map, ubiquitous language, aggregates, events, ACL contracts |
| `04-specs/` | SDD trio per feature (requirements + design + tasks) |
| `05-development/` | Worktree logs and branch↔task↔PR correlation |
| `06-design-system/` | Design System tokens, components, and patterns |
| `07-retrospectives/` | Sprint retros, PR code reviews, incidents + lessons learned |

Ops/deployment **outside** the vault (runbooks in Notion, alerts in Grafana). The vault only records *closed incidents*.

